<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nt ly ạlmn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉nt ly ạlmn ạldẖy ysẖbʿ qlby .. lạ yjwʿ ạlqlb ḥạsẖạ
 ḥbk ạlnhr ạldẖy yrwyny rby .. nfsy lạ tḥtạr ʿṭsẖy̱
 ạlqrạr- fyk mạ ạ̉rjw wạ̉ktẖr
 (ạ̉nt llnʿmạʾ mṣdr)2
 2- ạ̉nt ly ạlrạʿy ạldẖy yrʿy wjwdy .. lạ ykẖạf ạlqlb wḥsẖạ
 ạ̉nt ly ạlḥṣn wfyk kl jwdiⁿ .. mn ʿdạya lst ạ̉kẖsẖy̱
 3- fyk ly yạ sydy kl ạlkfạyẗ .. ạ̉nt yạ rby yswʿy
 fyk ly yạmnqdẖy kl ạlḥmạyẗ .. ạ̉nt yạ rạ̉sy ạlrfyʿi
 4- ạ̉nt fy ạlʿrsẖ lạ̉jly yạ sẖfyʿy .. tḍmn kl ḥyạty
 fyk kl ḥạjty rby yswʿy .. yạ mʿyny bl tẖbạty
 5- ạ̉yũ sẖkriⁿ yạ ḥbyby ywfy dyny .. yạ ạ̹lhy kyf ạ̉sẖkr
 ạ̉yũ ḥmdiⁿ ạ̉sẖdw ky ạ̉hdyk mny .. mhmạ kạn ạ̉nt ạ̉kbr</lyrics>
